    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ornamental areas of distinct pattern, material, color, or shape around the edge or boundary of something.  With regard specifically to tapestries, refers to the areas around the central field outside the inner guard and within the guard that edges the outer sides of the tapestry. For the narrow surfaces showing the 'thickness' or smallest dimension of thin, flat objects, as distinguished from the broad surfaces, see "edges (object components)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Áreas ornamentales de distinto modelo, material, color o forma alrededor del borde o límite de algo. Con respecto a los tapices específicamente, se refiere a las áreas alrededor del campo central fuera de la guarda interna y dentro de la guarda que bordea los lados exteriores del tapiz.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ornamentele gedeelten rondom de rand of begrenzing van een object, met patronen, materialen, kleuren of vormen die van het object zelf afwijken. Verwijst in specifieke zin naar de gedeelten van wandtapijten rond het centrale veld buiten de binnenste stroken en binnen de strook rond de buitenzijden van het wandtapijt. Zie 'randen (delen of aspecten van objecten)' voor de smalle delen van dunne, platte objecten met een zekere 'dikte' of de kleinste afmeting, ter onderscheiding van de brede oppervlakken.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Áreas ornamentais de padrão, material, cor 
ou forma distintos ao redor do borda ou limite 
de algo. No que diz respeito especificamente 
às tapeçarias, refere-se às áreas ao redor do
campo central fora da guarda interna e 
dentro da proteção que contorna os lados 
externos da tapeçaria. Para as superfícies
estreitas, que mostram a 'espessura' ou 
menor dimensão de objetos finos e planos, 
como distinto das superfícies amplas, 
consulte "arestas (componentes do objeto)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000316/CVAA-BR</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109633/CVAA-BR Consortium (2020-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>圍繞某物的邊緣或邊界的圖案、材質、顏色或形狀不同的裝飾區域。以掛毯而論，這尤其是指中央底部周遭、在保護內層之外並且在掛毯外側邊緣的保護外層之內的範圍。「邊 （物件局部）」則是指顯示出細薄、平坦物件的「厚度」或最小的範圍之狹窄表面，與寬廣的表面並不相同。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
